\chapter{Engineering Journey}
\label{ch:journey}
%==============================================================================

\section{The Chronological Build}
Pragya was built one module per session in a fixed dependency order, each tested via the interactive
\code{/docs} (or the UI) and git-committed before the next (Figure~\ref{fig:buildorder}).

\begin{figure}[h]
\centering
\begin{tikzpicture}[node distance=3.5mm and 7mm]
